WEBVTT

00:06:25.359 --> 00:06:31.191
maybe a kind that will never exactly,
in that form, come again.

00:06:31.215 --> 00:06:35.262
The formation of clouds
in the sky will never be the same

00:06:35.286 --> 00:06:37.000
as it is right now.

00:06:38.127 --> 00:06:40.591
Open your eyes. Look at that.

00:06:41.447 --> 00:06:43.447
(Music)

00:06:44.013 --> 00:06:47.169
Look at the faces of people whom you meet.

00:06:48.821 --> 00:06:53.053
Each one has an incredible story

00:06:53.077 --> 00:06:56.157
behind their face,

00:06:56.181 --> 00:07:00.732
a story that you could never fully fathom,